dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Dylan Wilson. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Angela. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is seven eight five six two.
Thank you, Angela. For security purposes, could you please confirm the last four digits of your social security number?
Yes, my social security number ends in four five six seven.
Great, thank you for verifying that information. How can I assist you today with Old Stone Auto Insurance, Angela?
I need to file a new claim for a recent accident I was involved in.
Of course, Angela. I will help you with that. Thank you for providing the necessary details. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help, Dylan.
You're welcome, Angela. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
